---
title: Cosy Coronation Chicken Pie with Mash Top, Peas and Mango Chutney
description: This Cosy Coronation Chicken Pie is perfect for autumn. The filling is inspired by the classic dish created for the coronation of Queen Elizabeth II, with a creamy curried sauce and sweet mango chutney, then topped with a layer of mash and grilled until golden and delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W44_UK_R12514-4_MAIN__11high-db1b5f0a.jpg
